snippet.textDisplay: The funny part for me is people who y’all the reveals but for those of us who have watched for years. I remember they announced the season 5 queens by releasing them in their boy drag looks and everyone said they were ugly and said the season looked like a flop. Then when season 6 came out, a lot of people thought the queens didn’t look ready for Drag Race. And they were actually really rough on Adore. They thought Bianca’s makeup was too much. And actually thought she wasn’t right for the show. And the front runners were Joslyn and April. And shall we not forget how everyone called Katya a Willam rip-off. The reason I’m saying this is learn from the past. Before every queen was THE queen, she was a queen performing in hometown bars just trying to create a name for themselves. And now they’re on the biggest platforms for Drag in the US. Move on.
